{"id": 956, "genre": 1000, "title": "你见过哪些对摄影技术的迷之自信？ ", "description": "现如今谁都能拍照，于是冒出了无数艺术家：拍得不好怪天怪地怪模特，拍得好看都叫天资过人技术好。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 3588, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130103wVhTpELurk2SJImB.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-04-27T01:00:50Z", "questions": [{"id": 840, "title": "你见过哪些对摄影技术的迷之自信？ ", "content": "你见过哪些对摄影技术的迷之自信？  ", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 69809, "content": "我照片照的不好都是因为没用单反", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125929Jw7vEKyS63hRknr1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 69810, "content": "拍花是老干部式微距，see，我会拍风景照", "image": "img/option/option/201607031259307w3FhEzmDJORoKn9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 69811, "content": "我会用黑白滤镜耶，是不是很快我就能去录艺术人生了", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183128AmlrNVIgWRKdn8OX.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 69812, "content": "同一张照片P成四种效果拼一起，我是Andy Warhol  ", "image": "img/option/option/201607021825175xA0C7Kkjeuts4Ph.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 69813, "content": "我换了个别人想不到（不想用）的歪歪的角度，超有意境的", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125930UHaD6bvzC2VE8Tqd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 69815, "content": "拍老人脸把锐度调最高，人文纪实我最棒", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182852yBLHAr3c9ejIGblW.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 69814, "content": "我人像拍不好都怪模特（你）太丑", "image": "img/option/option/20160703125930CTfglpreKFt09naR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 69816, "content": "“蛤又重来？这张拍得不是挺好的吗！”", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182900Njy5LkbuY87PnEW6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}